I"v<h1 id="header">Header</h1>

<p>Use the header to show users they are on an Essex County Council website and to provide tools to help them find what they need.</p>

<p>We have 2/3 versions of the header</p>

<ul>
  <li>the <a href="#default-header">deault header</a></li>
  <li>the header without search/navigation</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="default-header">Default header</h2>

<h2 id="when-to-use-the-default-header">When to use the default header</h2>

<p>Use the default header for Essex County Council web pages that use the Essex.gov.uk domain.</p>

<header class="header-background">
  <div class="header">
    <div class="nav">
      <div class="logo-wrap">
        <a href="/" class="logo-text seax">
          <img src="/public/images/seax.png" width="36" height="30" alt="Essex County Council logo" />
          Essex.gov.uk
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;header class="header-background"&gt;
  &lt;div class="header"&gt;
    &lt;div class="nav"&gt;
      &lt;div class="logo-wrap"&gt;
        &lt;a href="/" class="logo-text seax"&gt;
